---
title: Quick Chilli Jam-Glazed Fish with Creamy Asian Slaw, Peanuts & Mint
description: We’re doing fish with zap and zest tonight. Indulge in the pops of flavour when you take a bite of these dory fillets
glazed in a sweet chilli jam. A fresh slaw, creamy with mayo, rounds off the fish. Include a garnish of mint to the slaw
and a scattering of peanuts to the fish to really complete the blissful experience.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
